Package org.wikidata.wdtk.client

Command-line client to download dumps and serialize its data in several formats.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DumpProcessingAction
    This interface represents an action that may be performed with Wikibase dumps.
    DumpProcessingOutputAction.FinishableRunnable
    Simple interface for a Runnable that can be stopped gracefully by calling a method DumpProcessingOutputAction.FinishableRunnable.finish().
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Client
    This class provides a Java command line client to process dump files.
    ClientConfiguration
    This class handles the program arguments from the conversion command line tool.
    DumpProcessingOutputAction
    Abstract implementation of DumpProcessingAction that represents actions which generate outputs (in the form of files).
    JsonSerializationAction
    This class represents an action of generating a JSON dump from data.
    RdfSerializationAction
    This class represents an action of generating an RDF dump from data.
